Ralph Loop Codex Adaptation

This package includes compatibility files adapted from the official Anthropic
Claude Code ralph-loop plugin:

  https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/ralph-loop

The Codex runner, Codex manifest, Codex commands, tests, and documentation were
added in this repository to support Codex CLI and Codex App while keeping the
Claude Code plugin path functional.

